    "Due to the lack of domain knowledge in recommender systems, leveraging LLMs for item retrieval requires additional strategies such as model training, item indexing and grounding approaches [186].",
    "The prompt for matching tasks includes the description of a user in different forms, e.g., textual profiles and user-item interaction histories, in order to quickly match suitable items.• Ranking [92] in recommendation involves sorting or ordering items based on the predicted relevance or probability of interest to the target user.",
    "It aims to present the most relevant items at the top of the recommendation list.",
